{"tid":1853163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟香港人報唔報仇","createTime":"2020-01-30T20:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T22:01:42.000Z","uid":17802,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a561a551f48eaa3f931fb6c7d3572275f7adc336","tid":1853163,"uid":17802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T20:49:01.000Z","msg":"7.21嗌咗半年，打人嗰班全部無事。<br />\n今次又襲擊元朗居民，係咪又係無事"},{"pid":"2c4314736985f469837870c2a356f959ad041ca4","tid":1853163,"uid":17802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T21:01:15.000Z","msg":"7.21 之後大家話報仇， 7.27嗰時唔撚重狗咩？大家嘅反應係到時點樣打，而唔係話重狗唔出囉。<br />\n<br />\n今時今日已經唔祈求你哋做到D乜， 但係連人數都拎唔到出嚟，咁叫真係想做嘢嘅手足有咩辦法。<br />\n<br />\n連個抗爭環境同心態都無撚埋，一味諗住走精面，不如同個濕鳩政權投降，然後一齊集中營見啦，咪撚同我講煲底見。<br />\n<br />\n快撚D入嚟拉啦，叫yes sir啦"},{"pid":"a3ed866bdd6f8b77067352f74a358d569766e691","tid":1853163,"uid":125670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T21:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ff99ec3b3899810c3ac3fabb2323badd92f17b","tid":1853163,"uid":199902,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T21:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28cb06b9ea84283e58d350d1b71cc0bd3997760a","tid":1853163,"uid":17802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28ff99ec3b3899810c3ac3fabb2323badd92f17b","tid":1853163,"uid":199902,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T21:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T22:01:36.000Z","msg":"sad but true, 信咗3次， 3次都係咁"},{"pid":"cbdfcad9ef08851e30b68daa8a9e22f9798188e1","tid":1853163,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28ff99ec3b3899810c3ac3fabb2323badd92f17b","tid":1853163,"uid":199902,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T2